      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAFIA MISTRESS (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (20.53) in a Grade 6 at Angle Park. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Can atone. ASTON RAMONA (2) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (18.45) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Safe beginner and drawn well close to the inside. Can hit the frame this time. COMPTON LAYLA (8) did a good job to finish third last time out over 305m at this track (18.32) in a Other, the second top-three finish on the trot. Has good speed and will be prominent from out wide. Expected to do much better this time. MR. ZING ZANG (6) cannot be underestimated.",
